node.text:
We keep hearing about the importance of self-love, but what does that actually mean? You are about to find it by watching the video.☀️

My name is Dilara and I am a mindset coach. Having struggled with panic disorder, perfectionism and inability to love myself, I was never fully happy with who I am or my life, despite the success that I had at different stages. A series of events that have literally flipped my life upside down brought me to where I am today. I am grateful for all the experiences and I am now helping women to heal from difficult realtionships and build themselves up to be financially free. My programme is tailor made to meet individual needs and goals. During our first complimentary session I will get myself familiar with your story by asking you questions, followed by your questions for me, and at the end we will be deciding if we are good fit to work together.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
🌟 🌟 Due to collaboration with @dilaraaydyn you will get DISCOUNT CODE for her tailor made programme 🌻
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
DM @fullspiritquotes for DISCOUNT CODE ❤

30 days of @belindakitchenmaster Self love challenge ❤
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💡 Here on this link https://belindakitchenmaster.com/improveyoursenseofself
 you can find seven simple steps on how to learn to love yourself for free. 🙈🙉🙊
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Hey guys!🌟
I just wanted to share with you my impressions so far. 😃😃😃
For this 30 days I figured out lots of things about me that are very overwhelming. 😲
That I need to process, to figure out. All of that is part of growing, getting to know myself and becoming a better self every day🤩🤩🤩
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Here are some of the things that I worked on 😁😁😁😎
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
- I realized that I want to become more confident and fullfiled, especially with my talents, abillities and skills. 🤸‍♀🤹‍♀🚴‍♂
- I want to do more new things and expand my comfort zone.🏇🏄‍♂
-I want to give myself credit for my every achievement.👩‍🦰
-I improved my self care routine with some daily habits that will make me feel healthier and better about myself.🏋‍♀⛹️‍♀
-I examined belief about my body parts that I love and don't love so much. I'm working on embracing my whole body with all imperfections.🧘‍♀🧘‍♀🧘‍♀
-I became more aware about beliefs that are blocking me from living fullfiled life. 💆‍♀
- I started taking more responsibility for my  experiences 🐼🐼
- I started accepting change as something positive.🐣
-I started spending more time alone and feeling more comfortable with it.🧖‍♀
-I started talking more encouraging things to myself. 🗣💃
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Self love is a long, whole life journey with constant improvement, growing and embracing yourself. 🙋‍♀🙆‍♀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
So start that journey TODAY. 🌟
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Do that for yourself and your future self will thank you for it. ❤
